{"tid":613773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理乜尻名校secret，戴耀庭嚮香港自己地方俾左仔批鬥，但政府附和左仔，就冇人理？","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T10:33:43.000Z","uid":142888,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05987ba4897181c54a169422548dbaef937b3057","tid":613773,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"特區政府、中央政府、左報同建制派不斷追擊戴耀庭。好似之前大陸人舉報台灣歌手搞台獨咁，屌你老母，搞到最近我以為自己嚮大陸。英國佬去咗先20年，班左仔左妹就急不及待將大陸套政治風氣帶落嚟香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲台灣歌手俾大陸人舉報同批鬥，至少都可以返台灣搵食。香港人唔單止嚮大陸被大陸人舉報追擊，而家就連嚮香港自己地方都俾班左仔追擊批鬥，最重要係連香港特區政府都附和追擊佢，甚至叫港大革佢職<br />\n<br />\n你話佢損害言論自由，佢就同你講唔可以用言論自由做盾牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中華民國可以談論台獨，英國可以談論蘇格蘭獨立，香港本身都唔敏感，根本得大陸先敏感，但班左仔已經開壞先例將大陸套風氣帶落嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864414777f40ee40945d1794aecc3ec6edd2cea2","tid":613773,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde7b0b2422b7dd41ccd934d680a4eb486dce0ea","tid":613773,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2318bc8d46f0c23ccc5624d3e3352f36b57e5c14","tid":613773,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7159a095c67c4d74a7e9b21ae41937c252a63c9a","tid":613773,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20